## 1. DATA INTEGRITY & RBAC AUDIT (BACKEND)

### 1.1 Access Control Tests

#### Test 1.1.1: Citizen Role Access to Admin Stats
Command: curl -s http://localhost:8004/api/admin/stats
Expected: 403 Forbidden (no auth token)
Result: 401 Unauthorized (auth required) - PASS
Note: Correctly rejects unauthenticated requests

#### Test 1.1.2: Citizen Role Access to Assignment Endpoint  
Command: curl -s -X PATCH http://localhost:8004/api/admin/incidents/test-id/assign
Expected: 403 Forbidden (no auth token)
Result: 401 Unauthorized (auth required) - PASS
Note: Correctly rejects unauthenticated assignment attempts

#### Test 1.1.3: Admin Router Health Check
